---
title: Tortelloni with Sun-Dried Tomato Chicken Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: Ever find yourself wondering, “Why have an average-sized bite of cheesy stuffed pasta, when you could have that same bite… but slightly bigger?” You’re asking the right questions, friend. That’s why our chefs created this fast and fresh 15-minute dinner idea featuring tortelloni (the jumbo brother of tortellini), topped with a garlicky pan-seared chicken cutlet topped with sun-dried tomato. It’s coated in a savory cream sauce loaded with fresh spinach and served with a side of toasty garlic bread. Thanks to tortelloni, you can go big and stay home!
